{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready for the ultimate adrenaline rush in <strong><i>Hover REV Hispeed Burst!</i></strong> Set in a thrilling futuristic world, this high-speed racing game puts you on cutting-edge hover jet bikes capable of reaching near the speed of sound\u2014blazing through the skies at a jaw-dropping 1,000 km/h!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>RACE TRACKS</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Race on 24 awe-inspiring tracks that float high above the clouds, designed like colossal roller coasters with twists, loops, and hairpin curves that will push your reflexes to the limit that challenge even the most skilled racers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241440/extras/HoverGif600x252.gif?t=1739248214\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>TALENT RACERS</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take on the role of one of the talented and stylish anime-inspired racers, each with their unique personality and flair. These bold and competitive girls bring their A-game to the track, offering exciting rivalries and unforgettable moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241440/extras/HoverRev_SlideGif.gif?t=1739248214\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>GAME MODE</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Many game modes to choose from.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Championship</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Free arcade race</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Time attack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Elimination</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2 Players split screen</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Gold Trophy Award Evolution Cup","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steam